OL,3,CTUC in call for gender equality over
OL,4,Cpensions
OL,6,FRetired women effectively go more than
OL,7,Ffour months every year without getting
OL,8,Fa pension because of a gender gap,
OL,9,Faccording to research.
OL,11,FThe TUC estimated women were losing
OL,12,Fthe equivalent of #7,600 a year on
OL,13,Faverage.
OL,15,FThe union organisation said compared
OL,16,Fto men, retired women effectively stop
OL,17,Freceiving pension income from today.
OL,19,FThe income gap between men and women
OL,20,Fin retirement is now 36.5%, according
OL,21,Fto research from the Prospect union.
