OL,6,FThe Government has revived the Pension
OL,7,FCommission, which will bring together
OL,8,Funions, employer and independent
OL,9,Fexperts to look into the causes of the
OL,10,Fgap.
OL,12,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,13,F"Everyone deserves dignity and
OL,14,Fsecurity in retirement, but too many
OL,15,Fretired women have been left without
OL,16,Fenough to get by.
OL,18,F"We must make sure that these
OL,19,Finequalities are addressed for future
OL,20,Fgenerations.
