OL,6,F"That's why reviving the Pensions
OL,7,FCommission ` bringing together unions,
OL,8,Femployers and independent experts ` is
OL,9,Fa vital step forward.
OL,11,F"We now have a chance to make sure
OL,12,Feveryone, including women, receive the
OL,13,Fdecent retirement income that all
OL,14,Fworkers need."
OL,16,FA Government spokesperson said: "We're
OL,17,Fdetermined to close the gender
OL,18,Fpensions gap, and the new state
OL,19,Fpension has already reduced historic
OL,20,Finequalities faced by women and low
OL,21,Fearners.
